From 90e0a0153c77c89eaeed9be5173918046abb558c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Riajul Islam <opensource@example.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 10:13:07 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: rewrite terminal localhost links via VSCODE_PROXY_URI

When VSCODE_PROXY_URI is set (e.g. https://{{port}}.code.vk.community.example.com/),
terminal links like http://localhost:8000 are rewritten to the proxy URL
when clicked. The env var is read server-side, passed to the frontend
via UserSystemInfo, and used in a custom WebLinksAddon handler.

Handles localhost, 127.0.0.1, and 0.0.0.0 with any port.
---
 crates/server/src/routes/config.rs            |  2 ++
 .../src/shared/components/XTermInstance.tsx   | 25 ++++++++++++++++++-
 .../src/shared/hooks/useUserSystem.ts         |  2 ++
 .../shared/hooks/useUserSystemController.ts   |  4 +++
 shared/types.ts                               |  2 +-
 5 files changed, 33 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

